r the Great . It was also the name of one of Christ's apostles, of a deacon ordained by the apostles after the death of Christ, and of several other early saints.  See also  Philippa ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Philip Finamore was born about 1279, in Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, William Finamore, was 32 and his mother, Julyan Lovel, was 28. He had at least 1 son with Mrs. Philip Finamore."},"et":{"Abt 1279–":"umbes 1279–Surnud","1279–Male":"1279–Surnud","1282–Female":"1282–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1249–Male":"1249–Surnud","1253–Female":"1253–Surnud","1249":"1249","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1253":"1253","Abt 1279":"umbes 1279","1282":"1282","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1279–":"noin 1279–Kuollut","1279–Male":"1279–Kuollut","1282–Female":"1282–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1249–Male":"1249–Kuollut","1253–Female":"1253–Kuollut","1249":"1249","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1253":"1253","Abt 1279":"noin 1279","1282":"1282","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1279–":"environ 1279–Décédé","1279–Male":"1279–Décédé","1282–Female":"1282–Décédée","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1249–Male":"1249–Décédé","1253–Female":"1253–Décédée","1249":"1249","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1253":"1253","Abt 1279":"environ 1279","1282":"1282","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Philip Finamore est né environ 1279, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, William Finamore, avait 32 ans et sa mère, Julyan Lovel, avait 28 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Mrs. Philip Finamore."},"de":{"Abt 1279–":"um 1279–Verstorben","1279–Male":"1279–Verstorben","1282–Female":"1282–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1249–Male":"1249–Verstorben","1253–Female":"1253–Verstorben","1249":"1249","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1253":"1253","Abt 1279":"um 1279","1282":"1282","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Philip Finamore um 12